{"tid":874623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【釀裁員潮】中原地產本月恐蝕7000萬    200代理全年「零開單」","createTime":"2018-10-24T10:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T09:47:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"9cd70bc0fc5ab53ac387e3e0c95db0842d5098cb","tid":874623,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:33:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181024&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58830781\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181024%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58830781&d=oV03Jz3tVDaVEDGqvmAcKKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=6df89d59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181024%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58830781&h=c8fbcee4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181024&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58830781</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465e0cf7220e2961771e8c58fcf3ec8641165331","tid":874623,"uid":52942,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:37:58.000Z","msg":"fake news, 明明個個盤都爆飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6134c56ce23f0b0e9d803b0dfbe988c744f81c27","tid":874623,"uid":64009,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:42:27.000Z","msg":"係大陸挖人仔挖到傻啦佢地今年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係唔知點運番香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"041ee8d8cdc0779ba6e1dad72fe76b1121f7d813","tid":874623,"uid":22675,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:45:31.000Z","msg":"樓市嚴峻，地產代理處於水深火熱之中。本港龍頭代理之一的中原地產，有超過200名代理10個月未能開單，中原地產亞太區副主席兼住宅部總裁陳永傑指，該批代理有機會於年底遭解僱。<br />\n<br />\n中原陳永傑表示，公司每半年檢視一次代理成績，每名代理需要平均每月為公司進帳6.8萬元佣金。今年首十個月，中原地產有500名前線代理佣金收入不足10萬元，佔公司前線代理約一成人手，當中200人更「食白果」，於1至6月未能開單成交，全數至今亦是零成交，公司現時已發出嚴重警告信。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，如果該批代理至年底仍未開單，有機會全數被解僱。陳永傑亦引述集團主席施永青指，認為該批代理於年初至年中的旺市都開唔到單，相信於行業中很難生存。<br />\n<br />\n陳永傑指，樓市交投淡靜，公司10月至今佣金收入僅8,500萬元，較9月同期1.5億元有50%跌幅。預計全月佣金收入約1.5億至1.8億元，較上月全月2.6億，跌40%，業績有機會自今年2月以來首次「見紅」。他續稱，公司每月保本線為2.5億元，即本月恐蝕7,000萬元。此外，若本月佣金收入少於2億元，將創下2016年2月以來的超過兩年半新低。"},{"pid":"c8f02829393203638aeb8cadd34d819c9b3f1170","tid":874623,"uid":76216,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6134c56ce23f0b0e9d803b0dfbe988c744f81c27","tid":874623,"uid":64009,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:42:27.000Z","msg":"係大陸挖人仔挖到傻啦佢地今年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係唔知點運番香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:47:07.000Z","msg":"遊樂場代幣 冇得換返錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4642a1bdff3f56201cc01abe5e9196c9e30155","tid":874623,"uid":18465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c8f02829393203638aeb8cadd34d819c9b3f1170","tid":874623,"uid":76216,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6134c56ce23f0b0e9d803b0dfbe988c744f81c27","tid":874623,"uid":64009,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:42:27.000Z","msg":"係大陸挖人仔挖到傻啦佢地今年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係唔知點運番香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:47:07.000Z","msg":"遊樂場代幣 冇得換返錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:47:52.000Z","msg":"拎去掟彩虹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a847d914b28428b674242ba61ed8fa202c0f5d76","tid":874623,"uid":119502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"